{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"482788c9dd","title":"关於“统购统销”政策","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"0a52f170e4","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"482788c9dd"}],"tags":[{"id":"994fc035d4","name":"工业战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"879a0e7312","name":"吕庆仕"},{"id":"8d145154e0","name":"刘进仕"},{"id":"953e8a8781","name":"贠虎章"},{"id":"aaa5567602","name":"金宗仪"},{"id":"c6b6174392","name":"张森林"},{"id":"c71c3f3789","name":"党文蔚"},{"id":"e8bc734d52","name":"庚昌贵"},{"id":"ea25ac8f66","name":"西北农学院"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"845215c69f","type":"title","text":"关于“统购统销”政策","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"482788c9dd"},{"id":"25723d8c03","type":"authors","text":"西北农学院庚昌贵刘进仕党文蔚吕庆仕张森林金宗仪贠虎章","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"482788c9dd"},{"id":"4c209f77ee","type":"paragraph","text":"1．“大量农民移向城市是粮食统购统销的结果。”(畜60级学生　庚昌贵)","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"482788c9dd"},{"id":"4a017cdbe3","type":"paragraph","text":"2．“统购统销政府用低价收购农产品，农民吃亏。”(无名)","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"482788c9dd"},{"id":"054ba51f1a","type":"paragraph","text":"3．“在粮食统购统销中，干部硬逼着农民卖粮，硬叫把口粮卖出。”(农60级学生　刘进仕)","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"482788c9dd"},{"id":"e670963aa1","type":"paragraph","text":"4．“我害怕回家，回家后饿死。”“南方是产粮的，为什么没有粮吃，这是因为统购统完了。”(无名)","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"482788c9dd"},{"id":"d82a183316","type":"paragraph","text":"5．“在农村的余粮收购是揭农民的瓮底子。”(水58级学生  党文蔚)","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"482788c9dd"},{"id":"e4b58de796","type":"paragraph","text":"6．“统购统销使很多农民不够吃，有很多漏洞。”(植60级学生  吕庆仕)","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"482788c9dd"},{"id":"6098ccc711","type":"paragraph","text":"7．“卖余粮农民有自由，愿卖了就卖，不愿卖了就不卖，为啥硬叫农民卖余粮呢？”“我家原来每年出产的花生很多，收入很多钱，统购统销后，卖花生却没有自由。”(水58级学生　张森林)","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"482788c9dd"},{"id":"de5b3c68e4","type":"paragraph","text":"8．“国家对粮食和食油计划供应是党和国家限制了人民的物质方面的需要……是一种不合理的政策。”(林60级学生　金宗仪)","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"482788c9dd"},{"id":"a97d8f1c80","type":"paragraph","text":"9．“统购统销搞的太死了，人没零钱用，农产品收购价格太低了，工业品价格太高了。”(水58级学生　贠虎章)","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"482788c9dd"},{"id":"ce28ebc2c3","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：《西北农学院右派言论及错误言论汇集》(西北农学院马列主义教研组编印，1957年12月)。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"482788c9dd"}],"page":{"id":"8b31b99a65","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"482788c9dd","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}